name: Findproperty4u
body:
I am a Singapore real estate professional, and I can help you to choose the "right" property in Singapore - whether you are an experienced investor, a first time buyer or a foreigner looking to move into Singapore. My services cover you through the whole process - finding the property, negotiating the best price, making an offer and closing the deal. I am here to help you in everything to make the best real estate decision in your life.

I can be contacted via my mobile +65 9099 2260 or you can visit my website [Condo Singapore](http://www.findproperty4u.com) for details on Condominium projects / new launches in Singapore.
